comments: Noah (MEM) establishes himself in Aminu's (POR) path before the contact, extending his arms slightly, but allowing Aminu to move through the contact.
Conley (MEM) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
RAR shows Aminu (POR) extends his arm into Miles' (MEM) path but he is able to move through the contact.
Noah (MEM) establishes himself to Harkless' (POR) side and does not deliver contact.
Harkless (POR) makes contact to Conley's (MEM) body during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in legal position Conley's (MEM) path before the contact. The players tangle and then disengage.
Nurkic (POR) and Noah (MEM) briefly engage before the rebound attempt.
Nurkic (POR) moves into Conley's (MEM) path to establish a screen, but RATR shows there is no contact.
Nurkic (POR) moves into Bradley's (MEM) path to establish a screen, but RATR shows there is no contact.
Nurkic (POR) moves into Bradley's (MEM) path and delivers contact.
RAR shows Nurkic (POR) initially establishes a wide screening position in Bradley's (MEM) path but firms up over that leg before contact occurs to Bradley's lower body.
LLB shows Miles (MEM) makes hand on ball contact during Nurkic's (POR) shot attempt. Any deemed contact is considered incidental.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
Harkless (POR) and Noah (MEM) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Miles (MEM) places a hand to the side of Layman's (POR) hip at the start of the drive but does not affect his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) attempts to defend Bradley (MEM) closely, and when there is some contact, falls to the floor.
Harkless (POR) makes incidental contact to the arm of Conley (MEM) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Noah (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lillard (POR) and slightly extends his arms against him but he is able to move through contact.
Noah (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harkless (POR) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Replay confirms Harkless (POR) steps out of bounds with the ball and the shot clock is adjusted to 23 seconds reflecting the change in possession.
Lillard (POR) engages with Conley (MEM) during the screen but he is able to move throug contact.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a legal position in Conley's (MEM) path and firms up on his side but he is able to move through contact.
Noah (MEM) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Layman (POR) commits a take foul on Wright (MEM).
RAR shows Conley (MEM) is in a legal guarding position as Lillard (POR) leans into his body during his shooting motion.
